          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 173,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Animated statues usually appear in pairs or alone, hiding in plain sight among the other decor. Occasionally, a creator will fashion dozens of animated statues to serve as a nighunstoppable fighting force that doesn't complain or tire.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
